@startuml
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

title Doggy - Infrastructure Request Flow (Production, 15 stages)

actor User
participant "Web Browser" as Browser
participant "DNS" as DNS
participant "Platform Firewall" as Firewall
participant "Fly.io Edge" as Edge
participant "FastAPI Backend" as Api
participant "Dog Recognition Module\n(in-process)" as DogRec
participant "LLM API\n(Hugging Face / OpenRouter)" as Llm

User -> Browser: Upload image
Browser -> DNS: Resolve API host
DNS --> Browser: Endpoint resolved
Browser -> Firewall: HTTPS POST /api/dog-from-photo
Firewall -> Edge: Allow and pass request
Edge -> Api: Forward API request

Api -> DogRec: is_dog(image)
DogRec --> Api: Validation result
Api -> DogRec: predict_breed(image)
DogRec --> Api: raw_predictions
Api -> Llm: Generate advice (breed context)
Llm --> Api: Advice text
Api --> Edge: JSON {breed, advice, raw_predictions}
Edge --> Firewall: Forward response
Firewall --> Browser: Final response

note right of Browser
Dev mode:
Frontend calls backend via
VITE_API_BASE_URL directly.
end note

@enduml
